       000-PROC-SEC                SECTION.
      *
           INITIALIZE                  WRK-AREA
           INITIALIZE                  FLG-AREA
      *
      *    患者番号採番検索
           PERFORM 980-PTGETNUM-GET-SEC
           IF    FLG-KANRIMST      NOT =   ZERO
               MOVE    "1011"          TO  SPA-ERRCD
               DISPLAY "P012 SYS1009(PTGETNUM)ERR:" MCP-RC  "."
           END-IF
      *
           EVALUATE    ORCSP01-SYORI
      *        患者番号発行
               WHEN    "1"
               WHEN    "3"
                   PERFORM 100-HAKKOU-SEC
                           UNTIL    FLG-SYORI      =   1
      *        患者番号チェック
               WHEN    "2"
                   PERFORM 200-CHECK-SEC
           END-EVALUATE
